query:
SELECT ss.id, ss.companyId, ss.customDomain, ss.domainVerified, c.name as companyName, c.slug 
FROM site_settings ss 
JOIN companies c ON c.id = ss.companyId 
WHERE ss.customDomain IS NOT NULL;
